---
title: Beef Fillet Steak & Truffled Potato Dauphinoise with Green Beans & Honey Vinaigrette Salad
description: It’s not often that a perfectly cooked, tender beef fillet is upstaged by a side dish, but we think the potato dauphinoise might be the star of the show here! This classic French dish layers thinly sliced potatoes with rich cream, garlic, and a generous sprinkle of cheese. Every bite melts in your mouth, offering a comforting blend of flavuors that’s both elegant and irresistible.
